    "terms": [],
    "style_rules": [
      "Use US$ for U.S. dollar amounts.",
      "Keep listed-company annual report disclosure tone formal and publishable.",
      "Do not change numbers, percentages, years, named entities or financial metric values.",
      "For overview narrative, use full financial metric name plus abbreviation when provided.",
      "For financial review and business metrics narrative, use established abbreviations when provided.",
      "Prefer AIA China / AIA Hong Kong / AIA Macau over loose paraphrases when matched."
    ]
  },
  "current_unit": {
    "page_no": 13,
    "unit_id": "p13_g04",
    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 3,
    "source_text": "友邦保險具有多項顯著優勢，讓我們在競爭激烈的市場別樹一幟。我們在亞洲經營數十載，擁有區內無可比擬的\n平台，並於我們業務所在的大部分市場雄踞領導地位。我們始終如一地百分百專注於亞洲市場，有助我們在全球\n最具吸引力的壽險業地區全面把握增長機遇。這份專注結合我們領導團隊在亞洲的豐富經驗及員工的優秀質素，",
    "current_translation": "AIA possesses multiple distinctive competitive advantages that set us apart in a highly competitive market. With decades of operations across Asia, we have an unparalleled platform in the region and hold leading market positions in most of the markets where we operate. Our unwavering 100% focus on the Asian market enables us to fully capitalize on growth opportunities in the world's most attractive life insurance region. This focus, combined with our leadership team's extensive experience in Asia and our employees' exceptional capabilities,"
  },
  "output_format": {
    "translations": [
      {
        "unit_id": "p13_g04",
        "translation": "<更紧凑译文>"
      }
    ]
